casebody.data:
No. 11-5731. Assem A. Abulkhair, Petitioner v. Edward W. Boehm, et al. 565 U.S. 1011, 132 S. Ct. 550,

181 L. Ed. 2d 393,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8070. November 7, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of New Jersey dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
